Invocation Name: fluid philosophy
des: These philosophical musings are some of the helpful information I have been given by aliens, stuff I have known all along, stuff I learned from animals and plants, and wisdom from the future which I have not yet learned. Why not listen to a few and see what your reaction is? Time is an illusion so what have you got to lose by trying? I'm sure you will feel better after you realize that your entire reality is within your control. Stay curious!
